@startuml
title BP-16 - Bulk Bill Generation

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Select payment product;
:Select multiple students;
:Input period and due date;

|Platform|
:Remove duplicate student IDs from request;
:Validate student list is not empty;
:Validate payment product belongs to tenant;
:Begin transaction;

|Billing Engine|
:Validate each student belongs to tenant;
:Check duplicate obligation for each student;

if (Any validation failed?) then (Yes)
  :Rollback transaction;
  :Return validation error;
  stop
else (No)
  :Create obligations for all selected students;
endif

|Platform|
:Commit transaction;

|Finance Officer|
:Review bulk generation result;
stop

note right
Current endpoint:
POST /student-obligations/bulk
Business rule:
The whole batch should succeed or fail together.
end note
@enduml
